# Input

```scss
$beforeTrailingCommaComment:(a:b /* before */,);
$trailingBlockComment:(a:b,/* end */);
$multipleTrailingBlockComments:(a:b,/* end */ /* more */);
$ownLineTrailingBlockComment:(a:b,
/* end */
);
$trailingLineComment:(a:b,// end
);
$commentedNestedMapValue:(key:(other-key:other-other-value),/* end */);
$emptyBlockCommentMap:(/* comment */);
$emptyLineCommentMap:(// comment
);

```


# Formatted

```scss
$beforeTrailingCommaComment: (
	a: b /* before */,
);
$trailingBlockComment: (
	a: b, /* end */
);
$multipleTrailingBlockComments: (
	a: b, /* end */
	/* more */
);
$ownLineTrailingBlockComment: (
	a: b,
	/* end */
);
$trailingLineComment: (
	a: b, // end
);
$commentedNestedMapValue: (
	key: (
		other-key: other-other-value,
	), /* end */
);
$emptyBlockCommentMap: (/* comment */);
$emptyLineCommentMap: (
	// comment
);

```
